<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>مَعْرِفَةُ التَّابِعِينَ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>والتَّابعِيُّ اللاَّقِي لِمَنْ قَدْ صَحِبَا ...<span class="c5"> وَلِلْخَطِيبِ حَدُّهُ:</span> أنْ يَصْحَبَا<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>